        <updateDate>2019-11-05T18:48:00Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Bolts Ditch Access and Use Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Agriculture to permit by special use authorization nonmotorized access and use of the Bolts Ditch headgate and the Bolts Ditch within the Holy Cross Wilderness in Colorado for the diversion of water and use, maintenance, and repair of the ditch and headgate by the town of Minturn, Colorado.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
